{{translation|Mount Katsuragi|葛城山|Katsuragizan}} is a mountain which holds the Tsuchigumo clan's kinjutsu. Hotaru and Tonbee live on this mountain. To prevent any intruders from obtaining the kinjutsu, the mountain is surrounded by a seemingly unbreakable barrier and protected by a large amount of traps. The Magaki Group managed to break the barrier from the inside and evade all the traps successfully.

